{"tid":2350042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽坐月半個月揭老公包養PTGF超崩潰","createTime":"2021-01-02T04:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T04:48:20.000Z","uid":141988,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d30b7a2e53c9bcdb6b8dffbbdd174366dc279f88","tid":2350042,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"邊位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近日有港媽在討論區上分享，指自己近年為了與老公生細仔而多次接受人工受孕，「夾埋打咗100針」，今年才終於成功並順利產子。不料坐月期間卻發現老公數年前已經長期包養PTGF（兼職女友），港媽聲言即使「證據確鑿」，老公仍死口否認。港媽坦言自己「好傻好白癡」，不知如何是好，「個腦一片空白」，希望網民可以給予意見。<br />\n<br />\n港媽在留言中回覆網民提問時表示，自己沒有因為人工受孕而忽略老公，「一直都有性行為」，甚至是主動的一方，「我真係唔明點解咁仲唔滿足」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/564761/%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%BD%E6%89%93%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E9%87%9D%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%97%E5%AD%95%E8%AA%95%E7%AC%AC2%E8%83%8E-%E5%9D%90%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%8A%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%8F%AD%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%8C%85%E9%A4%8Aptgf%E8%B6%85%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F564761%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E9%2587%259D%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AD%2595%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%25AC%25AC2%25E8%2583%258E-%25E5%259D%2590%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%258F%25AD%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258C%2585%25E9%25A4%258Aptgf%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb08eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=2ceccd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/564761/%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%BD%E6%89%93%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E9%87%9D%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%97%E5%AD%95%E8%AA%95%E7%AC%AC2%E8%83%8E-%E5%9D%90%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%8A%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%8F%AD%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%8C%85%E9%A4%8Aptgf%E8%B6%85%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"htt